{"tid":2037021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"吳靄儀：《國安法》設立內地駐港國安機構是直接違反《基本法》第22條","createTime":"2020-05-26T20:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T01:17:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d453acae44953e7e1ba8359c448d9b345e826b65","tid":2037021,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T20:17:07.000Z","msg":"吳靄儀指：「我在我的社交平台寫段文字是否算是(犯罪)行為？在我是言論自由，在你是犯罪行為。為何要有22條，中央的執法機關不可到港執法。現在你即是撕毀一切、即是食言。香港人其實只需要保障起碼的自由，你不要搞香港，香港人就不會做激烈的事。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5eccf41734b03149130b4895/政府指港區國安法無礙各項權利自由-吳靄儀憂增對中央不信任\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5eccf41734b03149130b4895%2F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8C%87%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E7%84%A1%E7%A4%99%E5%90%84%E9%A0%85%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1-%E5%90%B3%E9%9D%84%E5%84%80%E6%86%82%E5%A2%9E%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E4%B8%8D%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=4fca010e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5eccf41734b03149130b4895/政府指港區國安法無礙各項權利自由-吳靄儀憂增對中央不信任</a><br />\n<br />\n可惜, 香港法官曾經判過：人大是至最無上, 等同上帝, 可以違反任何嘢都OK"},{"pid":"4ec9b7b6a60e2e16bdc15fb0be7153125ffdc6f4","tid":2037021,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T20:21:15.000Z","msg":"馬道立表示，法庭往往要在各種合法卻互相矛盾的訴求中，作出平衡考慮。他以《人權法》第17條對和平集會自由的保障為例，指出和平集會的權利與言論自由息息相關，然而這自由並非毫無約制：「（人權法）第17條規定，和平集會的權利，在依法律的規定，並在<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">維護國家安全</span></span>或公共安寧、公共秩序、維持公共衞生或風化、或保障他人權利自由所必要時，可以受到限制。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/馬道立-司法獨立至爲重要-集會自由非毫無限制/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%93%E7%AB%8B-%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%87%B3%E7%88%B2%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81-%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%9D%9E%E6%AF%AB%E7%84%A1%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%2F&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=71cad228\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%93%E7%AB%8B-%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%87%B3%E7%88%B2%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81-%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%9D%9E%E6%AF%AB%E7%84%A1%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%2F&h=b2e353b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/馬道立-司法獨立至爲重要-集會自由非毫無限制/</a>"},{"pid":"ae1aef18ac62bbdd79b0df04842db51573b71f43","tid":2037021,"uid":265628,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T22:07:27.000Z","msg":"你老母到而家都講法治，你私人協控左未呀。 <br />\n日撚日呃香港人deadbody，日撚日唔善用法律。<br />\n成年得 許智峄有吉士去告，其他就關自己事先告。"},{"pid":"92b46c534b14fd610819add2f384c6bd6f08dc99","tid":2037021,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T23:57:10.000Z","msg":"醒未呀<br />\n屌你老母大愛左膠<br />\n依家仲講法治！？<br />\n過去一年d畫面仲未夠呀？"},{"pid":"d9699ee2c7669da3858cd725d911de72f61138e6","tid":2037021,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:04:26.000Z","msg":"So what?"},{"pid":"8ec9a3794c392cc8c92467943e3af54f9554ecf1","tid":2037021,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:06:13.000Z","msg":"新法優於舊法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b714fe779c3b48783f33ca51d974117cc97992","tid":2037021,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:27:19.000Z","msg":"中共：人大就係法律，完"},{"pid":"08055b9f06994fd2c2fcccb9b8ba1ca71284ae90","tid":2037021,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:42:45.000Z","msg":"重基本法，笑撚左，笑埋右"},{"pid":"68915cfa00369a6e78eafe502de180ee24d26e5e","tid":2037021,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61b714fe779c3b48783f33ca51d974117cc97992","tid":2037021,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:27:19.000Z","msg":"中共：人大就係法律，完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:43:14.000Z","msg":"習近平就係法